parameters.name: ENERGY
parameters.description: Energy for row.  Value is not used

parameters.name: ESA_DAC
parameters.description: ESA DAC for row; used to select contiguous rows for linear interpolation, and for the calculation of the interpolation.

parameters.name: RPA_DAC
parameters.description: RSA DAC for row; if the RSA_DAC value for one of a pair of rows being used for interpolation is zero, use the background for the other member of the pair.

parameters.name: PCEM_BACK
parameters.description: Backgound count rate for row for PCEM background subtraction - Units are counts * R(Sun,AU)**2 / sample

parameters.name: SCEM_BACK
parameters.description: Backgound count rate for row for SCEM background subtraction - Units are counts * R(Sun,AU)**2 / sample

parameters.name: COIN_BACK
parameters.description: Backgound count rate for row for COIN background subtraction - Units are counts * R(Sun,AU)**2 / sample
